Class IFloppyDrive

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox.VBoxObject
      com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox.IFloppyDrive

public class IFloppyDrive
extends VBoxObject

The IFloppyDrive interface represents the virtual floppy drive of the virtual machine. An object of this type is returned by IMachine#floppyDrive.
